Citation.sTitle: Densities and Excess Molar Volumes of Cyclopentane (1) + 1-Alkanol (2) Systems at (298.15 and 308.15) K
Citation.sAbstract: Densities for binary mixtures of cyclopentane with 1-propanol, 1-pentanol, and 1-heptanol over the whole composition range have been measured at temperatures (298.15 and 308.15) K. From these densities, excess molar volumes were calculated. All the experimental excess molar volumes were fitted to the Redlich-Kister equation.
